Description.
Body length (measured from the apex of clypeus to the elytral end): ď, 9.78–10.79 mm (mean ± SD; 10.31±0.27 mm; n= 
11
); Ψ, 10.48–11.35 mm (mean ± SD; 10.97±0.32 mm; n= 
